In a skillet, over medium-high heat, add oil and chicken. When chicken is browned, add lemon slices, onions, and red bell pepper. Then continue to cook for 2 to 3 minutes. Remove lemon slices and put them on a plate for later. Stir in UNCLE BEN'S(R) Flavor Infusions Roasted Chicken Rice and water. Bring to boil, then reduce to medium heat and simmer covered for 15 minutes or until water is absorbed. Stir in lemon slices and garnish with parsley. Enjoy!